      <br>
      <p class="text-1"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Milk and dairy products:</span> Plastic function. They participate in the formation and maintenance of the different structures of the organism. They are protein foods and their energetic power depends on the fat that accompanies the proteins.</p>
