      <br>
      <p class="text-1"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Meat, fish and eggs:</span> Plastic function. They are foods that incorporate proteins of high biological power, iron and vitamins of the B group. Meat and fish proteins are equally necessary, although fish is considered healthier due to its omega-3 fat content. Eggs are also rich in essential nutrients.</p>
      <a class="a-2" href="/products/group2">Create Product</a>
