      <br>
      <p class="text-1"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Fruits:</span> Regulatory function. Their importance in the diet is similar to that of group 4, vegetables, and they are also rich in sugars such as sucrose, fructose and glucose, but with a low calorie content.</p>
      <a class="a-2"  href="/products/group5">Create Product</a>
      <br>
    </div>
