      <br>
      <p class="text-1"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Cereals and derivatives, sugar and sweets:</span> Energy function. They provide calories from their carbohydrates (those of cereals are denser and more nutritious than other sources of carbohydrates). Also important is the contribution of group B vitamins.</p>
      <a class="a-2"  href="/products/group6">Create Product</a>
      <br>
